rotherhood: Allah helps him as long as he helps his brother","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever relieves the hardship of a believer in this world, Allah will relieve his hardship on the Day of Resurrection. Whoever helps ease one in difficulty, Allah will make it easy for him in this world\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13000,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/heavens-earth-praise-scholars\/","url_meta":{"origin":22127,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Heaven and earth praise seekers of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever travels a path in search of knowledge, Allah will make him traverse a path to Paradise. Verily, the angels lower their wings in pleasure for the seeker of knowledge. The inhabitants of the heavens and earth, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/11\/99-names-allah-asma-al-husna\/","url_meta":{"origin":22127,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on 99 Names: Whoever acts upon them enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has ninety-nine names. Whoever preserves\u00a0them will enter Paradise.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7392, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2677 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/02\/la-hawla-wa-la-quwwata-illa-billah\/","url_meta":{"origin":22127,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: No movement or might but in Allah, treasure of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cShall I not tell you about a word among the treasures of Paradise?\u201d I said, \u201cOf course.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThere is no movement or might but in Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2704\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/16\/path-to-paradise-or-hell\/","url_meta":{"origin":22127,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Paradise surrounded by hardship, Hellfire by desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 16, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cParadise is surrounded by adversity,\u00a0and Hellfire is surrounded by lusts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2823 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0641\u064e\u0651\u062a\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u062d\u064f\u0641\u064e\u0651\u062a\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/akhirah-laugh-less-weep-more\/","url_meta":{"origin":22127,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: If you could see, you will cry more and laugh little","author":